verbose_text: Use of a previously validated morpholino to cxcl8 attenuated the shift in the fraction of embryos with elevated runx / cmyb expression (XREF_FIG) as well as the boost in Flk1 + cMyb + HSPCs mediated by 1,25 (OH) D3 (con versus 1,25 (OH) D3, p < 0.05; con versus cxcl8 MO, N.S.; cxcl8 MO versus cxcl8 MO + 1,25 (OH) D3, N.S.; 1,25 (OH) D3 versus 1,25 (OH) D3 + cxcl8 MO, N.S.
